WEBVTT

00:00:00.151 --> 00:00:04.256
Your responses to complex challenges are heavily dictated by your personal values.

00:00:04.877 --> 00:00:09.763
Authentic leaders exhibit consistency among their values, their beliefs, and their actions.

00:00:10.224 --> 00:00:14.089
When your thoughts, feelings and behaviors align, you are leading with congruence.

00:00:14.670 --> 00:00:16.452
Congruence is the gravity of leadership.

00:00:16.933 --> 00:00:22.600
It grounds you in your values, provides stability for your team, allows others to predict how you will act,

00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:24.963
and fundamentally builds shared trust.
